        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='20332' hidden='true' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='48524' x='3937' y='20539'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>This results help to examines the differences in sleep duration, screen use, and work patterns between urban and rural residents in Bhutan to understand how these lifestyle factors influence overall health and wellbeing. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='17427' hidden='true' id='7' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='43799' x='53642' y='39419'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI'>Take care of yourself first</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI' italic='true'>or you will have nothing left to give others.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI'>Self-care is not selfishness.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI' italic='true'>You cannot serve it from an empty vessel.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='8' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='21457' x='37598' y='14834'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontsize='16'>Health and Wellbeing</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='57365' id='9' story-point-id='8' type-v2='text' w='35335' x='63976' y='14730'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Urban and rural residents in Bhutan show the biggest difference in work hours, while screen use and sleep time are almost the same.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Urban residents work about 6.12 hours per day, while rural residents work 5.64 hours meaning urban residents work around 29 minutes more on average. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Screen use before sleep is slightly higher in rural areas with 2.16 compared to urban areas with 1.98, but the difference is very small, showing that both groups have similar digital habits before bedtime.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'> Sleep duration is also almost the same, with rural residents sleeping 7.09 hours and urban residents 7.03 hours on average.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{9B2190AB-4D2B-488C-A482-4CEBBCBCF4DA}' />
